channel.description:
Hazzscape || Pets ★ All Skills ★ All PvMs ★ 24/7 ★ GE and More!
Website- www.hazzscape.weebly.com
Download Client on the homepage ("www.hazzscape.weebly.com") - or Dropbox Link: ("https://dl-web.dropbox.com/get/Hazzscape.jar?_subject_uid=84878093&w=AABNY2PVLobj5RySh9d4haYgZh65lFIqB60W6XkYWCyx3Q") I DO have a webclient and its at "http://www.hazzscape.weebly.com/webclient.html" but for some people its not loading and that's causes by the java or god knows what but the client works link above to download the Client.
[url=http://www.upload.ee/image/4763288/Home.png][img]http://www.upload.ee/thumb/4763288/Home.png[/img][/url] Lovely Home of hazzscape! the home before was at clan camp and edge but i gotta say this some look SEXY!
[url=http://www.upload.ee/image/4763291/GE.png][img]http://www.upload.ee/thumb/4763291/GE.png[/img][/url] Yes! There is grandexchange. took me forever to add but i did get there! buying and selling 110% like runescape i love it :), but like i said works 110% like runescape .. yes a player must be selling the item for you to buy it so i have added shops aswell incase you cant buy an item that your looking for.
[url=http://www.upload.ee/image/4763292/Pins.png][img]http://www.upload.ee/thumb/4763292/Pins.png[/img][/url] Added bank pins make sure u add a pin for security reasons!
[url=http://www.upload.ee/image/4763294/Teleports.png][img]http://www.upload.ee/thumb/4763294/Teleports.png[/img][/url] Lovely spirit tree teleports at the home of hazzscape! Minigames teles : SoulWars [url=http://www.upload.ee/image/4763295/soulwars.png][img]http://www.upload.ee/thumb/4763295/soulwars.png[/img][/url], Duel Arena, Pest Control, Dungeoneering, Fight Kiln, Fight Caves, Recipe for Disaster, RuneSpan, Dominion Tower, Barrows, Castle Wars and Warriors Guild!. Skilling Teles: Fishing Guild, Mining Teleports, Agility teleports, Woodcutting, Runecrafting, Summoning, Farming teleports, Hunter, Pyramid Plunder, firemaking and Sawmill (Basic) Training Teles: Rock Crabs, Taverley Dungeon [Black Demons], Armoured Zombies, Yaks and Mature grotworms! Boss Teles (on next page) All Godwars bosses Including Nex! [url=http://www.upload.ee/image/4763296/NEx.png][img]http://www.upload.ee/thumb/4763296/NEx.png[/img][/url] Tormented Demons, Corp YES Everything u can think of! Kalphite Queen, QBD, Bork, Barrelchest, Dag Kings, etc!
Switch items looks! if you dont like how an item is looking ::switchitemslook for new/old looks! - [url=http://www.upload.ee/image/4763297/switchitemslook.png][img]http://www.upload.ee/thumb/4763297/switchitemslook.png[/img][/url]
What are you waiting for? Join NOW! [url=http://www.upload.ee/image/4763298/join.png][img]http://www.upload.ee/thumb/4763298/join.png[/img][/url] Also Lending items work! didnt take a picture because nobody was online.
Owner Hazz || Hazzscape Skype - h4zz4n1 if you are intrested on becoming a hazzscape moderator :-)
